      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-text mj-class="section_header">
            <h3>
              <!-- htmlmin:ignore --><a name="care"></a><!-- htmlmin:ignore -->BES Care
            </h3>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-spacer height="20px" />
          <mj-text>
            <h3>If you would like help coming to shul events, we have volunteers who can drive you. Please contact Karen on <a href="tel:07341005116">07341 005 116</a>, if you would like help with transport.</h3>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-spacer height="20px" />
          <mj-divider />
          <mj-text>
            <p class="title">If you or someone you know may benefit from support, please reach out in confidence to our professional Community Support Coordinator Karen on <a href="tel:07341005116">07341 005 116</a> / <a href="mailto:care@borehamwoodshul.org">care@borehamwoodshul.org</a></p>
            <p class="title">Volunteering</p>
            <p>If you are interested in volunteering for BES Care, we have a variety of opportunities available, including befriending, driving, delivering food parcels and more.</p>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-button href="mailto:care@borehamwoodshul.org">Join the BES Care Volunteer Team</mj-button>
          <mj-spacer height="10px" />
          <mj-image src="https://borehamwoodshul.org/assets/uploads/2024/02/BESCare-Here-to-help.png" />
          <mj-text>
            <p>
              <strong>BES Care are delivering essential food items to many people in the community. If this would be a helpful support for you, please contact Karen on <a href="tel:07341005116">07341 005 116</a> or email <a href="mailto:care@borehamwoodshul.org">care@borehamwoodshul.org</a>.</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="title">Hardship Fund</p>
            <p>Our confidential Hardship Fund provides financial support and food vouchers to people in the community. The numbers who need our help has doubled in the past few years as people are struggling to pay their bills and buy food and clothes.</p>
            <p>We want to be able to help everyone who needs and ask those members who can donate to please offer their support. Referrals are continuing to increase as people are worried about paying for food and heating.</p>
          </mj-text>
          <mj-button href="https://www.justgiving.com/fundraising/borehamwood-hardship-fund">Please help by donating what you can.</mj-button>
          <mj-spacer height="20px" />
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      <mj-section>
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text mj-class="section_header">
            <h3>
              <!-- htmlmin:ignore --><a name="yahrzeits"></a><!-- htmlmin:ignore -->We wish long life to those observing a Yahrzeit from 2 - 8 May
            </h3>
